==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mattock
<hw>Mat"tock</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>mattuc</ets>; cf. W. <ets>matog</ets>.]</ety> <def>An implement for
digging and grubbing. The head has two long steel blades, one like an
adz and the other like a narrow ax or the point of a pickax.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>'T is you must dig with <qex>mattock</qex> and with spade.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mattoid</ent>⟦br⟧
